dding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">3. 모집일정</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  가. 접수기간 : 2026.4.10.(금) ~ 4.24.(금) 17:00까지</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  나. 영어인터뷰 : 신청서 접수 이후 전화인터뷰 진행 (개별연락)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">4. 참가신청</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0naHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmcnIHdpZHRoPScxMCcgaGVpZ2h0PScxMCc+ADxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPScxMCcgaGVpZ2h0PScxMCcAIGZpbGw9ACcjZmZmZmZmJyBmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk9ACcxJy8+ADwvc3ZnPg==\"); line-height: 23.4667px;'>가. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">‘</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.09em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">참가신청서’, ‘지원자정보 입력양식’</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.05em; line-height: 23.4667px;\"> 글로벌교류팀 이메일 </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">제출</span><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0naHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmcnIHdpZHRoPScxMCcgaGVpZ2h0PScxMCc+ADxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPScxMCcgaGVpZ2h0PScxMCcAIGZpbGw9ACcjZmZmZmZmJyBmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk9ACcxJy8+ADwvc3ZnPg==\"); line-height: 23.4667px;'>(outbound1@dongguk.edu)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">   나. 해당 프로그램 웹사이트 온라인 등록</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">    1) GCS 미국 뉴욕 인턴십 웹사이트 : globalcareersolution.com/27</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">    2) ICDC Korea 미국 인턴십 웹사이트 : www.icdckorea.com/USA02</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt