1pt; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">로</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">      </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">하</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">여, 파견학기 본교 등록 시 최대 18학점(정규학기 12학점+계절학기 6학점), 휴학 시 최대</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">      3학점(계절학기)까지 학점 인정(전</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">공</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 23.4667px;\"> </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">또는 자선, P/F)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  나. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0.01em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">파견학기 본교 등록자 중, 근무개시일이 2026년 10월 이후이거나 2026-2학기 정규학기</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">     </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.08em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">기간 중 총 근무기간이 16주 640시간을 충족시키지 못할 경우, 최대 15학점 인정</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.08em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">      (정규학기 9학점</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">+계절학기 6학점)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  다. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">전공(복수전공)학점은 소속 전공(복수전공)학과 주임교수 승인 시에만 인정하며,</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\"> 학과</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">에서 전</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">     공</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">으로 인정하지 않을 경우 자선(자유선택) 학점으로 인정</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  라. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">재학 중 통산하여 국내 현장실습 및 글로벌 현장실습(해외인턴십)을 통해 취득 가능한 학점은</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">   </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">최대 18학점(전공 최대 12학점)이</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">며, 기존에 국내 또는 국외 </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">현장실습 학점을 취득한 경우,</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">     </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">18학점에서 해당 취득학점을 차감한</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\"> 만큼만 </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">학점취득이 가능</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">6. 문 의</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  가.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\"> 학사 및</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 23.4667px;\"> 학점관련 : 신공학관 9층 글로벌교류팀(02-2260-3464)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 23.4667px;\">  나. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">근무회사 및 업무, 참가비용, 현지생활, 비자관련</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 74.9pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -72.4pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">    1) Global Carrer Solution(GCS) : (070-8028-3015, chlee@gcsloution.co.kr)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 74.9pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -72.4pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">    2) 국제경력개발원(ICDC) : (02-3453-9110, </span><a href=\"mailto:info@icdckorea.com\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 23.4667px;\">info@icdckorea.com</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 74.9pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -72.4pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 23.4667px;\">    3) ICCE Korea : (02-335-7755, tommy@iccekorea.com)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 74.9pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -72.4pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 